menuconfig DRIVERS_IMU_DAMIAO_DMIMU_L1
	bool "DM-IMU L1 CAN driver"
	default n
	---help---
		Enable support for Damiao IMU L1 via CAN bus.

		This driver supports:
		- Accelerometer and gyroscope data
		- Attitude (Euler angles and quaternions)
		- Active and request modes
		- Sensor calibration
		- Parameter configuration
